PF 的不透明 AI Agent 运行时可观测与执行控制：超越沙箱与审批","href":"/zh/blog/2026/05/25/runtime-security-for-ai-agents/","depth":0},{"title":"CPU 噪声会拖慢 GPU 推理吗：用 eBPF 定量测量调度器与 IRQ 影响","href":"/zh/blog/2026/05/24/measuring-cpu-noise-in-gpu-inference-with-ebpf/","depth":0},{"title":"ACRFence：防止 AI Agent 检查点恢复中的语义回滚攻击","href":"/zh/blog/2026/05/21/acrfence-preventing-semantic-rollback-attacks-in-agent-checkpoint-restore/","depth":0},{"title":"AgentCgroup：当 AI 编程 Agent 遇到操作系统资源","href":"/zh/blog/2026/02/17/agentcgroup-what-happens-when-ai-coding-agents-meet-os-resources/","depth":0},{"title":"Reverse Engineering Claude Code's SSL Traffic with eBPF","href":"/zh/blog/2026/02/13/reverse-engineering-claude-codes-ssl-traffic-with-ebpf/","depth":0},{"title":"A Taxonomy of GPU Bugs: 19 Defect Classes for CUDA Verification","href":"/zh/blog/2026/01/29/a-taxonomy-of-gpu-bugs-19-defect-classes-for-cuda-verification/","depth":0},{"title":"智能体系统架构：隔离、集成与治理的综合调研","href":"/zh/blog/2026/01/11/architectures-for-agent-systems-a-survey-of-isolation-integration-and-governance/","depth":0},{"title":"GPU可观测性差距：为什么我们需要卸载到GPU设备上的eBPF","href":"/zh/blog/2025/10/14/the-gpu-observability-gap-why-we-need-ebpf-on-gpu-devices/","depth":0},{"title":"NVIDIA Open GPU Kernel Modules Comprehensive Source Code Analysis","href":"/zh/blog/2025/10/14/nvidia-open-gpu-kernel-modules-comprehensive-source-code-analysis/","depth":0},{"title":"Understanding iaprof: A Deep Dive into AI/GPU Flame Graph Profiling","href":"/zh/blog/2025/10/11/understanding-iaprof-a-deep-dive-into-ai-gpu-flame-graph-profiling/","depth":0},{"title":"AgentSight: 让 AI Agent 的一举一动都在掌控之中，基于 eBPF 的系统级可观测性方案","href":"/zh/blog/2025/08/26/agentsight-keeping-your-ai-agents-under-control-with-ebpf-powered-system-observability/","depth":0},{"title":"Profiling and Tracing Tools Across System Layers and Architectures","href":"/zh/blog/2025/08/20/profiling-and-tracing-tools-across-system-layers-and-architectures/","depth":0},{"title":"The Modern Memory Testing Arsenal -- A